'''tender''' (plural: [[tenders]])

#A type of [[payment]] such as a [[check]], cash or by credit card.
#:"Your [[credit card]] has been declined, you need to provide alternate ''tender'' such as cash, check or a different card."
#A [[railroad]] car towed behind a steam engine to carry fuel.
#A naval [[ship]] that functions as a mobile base for other ships. (''submarine tender'', ''destroyer tender'')

===Verb===
'''tender''' ([[tendered]], tendered)
#To offer as payment

